# fold: sum-of-squares via reduce-style HOF.
*fold(xs as Vec of i64, init as i64, f as (i64, i64) returns i64) returns i64
    acc is init
    i is 0
    while i < xs.length
        acc is f(acc, xs.get(i))
        i is i + 1
    acc

*main
    xs is vec()
    i is 1
    while i <= 5
        xs.push(i)
        i is i + 1
    log fold(xs, 0, |a, x| a + x * x)
